<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Welcome Email</title>
    <style>
      /* Reset styles for email compatibility */
      body,
      table,
      td,
      a {
        -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;
        -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        border: 0;
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      }

      /* Main container */
      .email-container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #f9f9f9;
        border: 1px solid #ddd;
      }

      /* Header */
      .header {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 20px 0;
        background-color: #007bff;
        color: #ffffff;
      }

      .header h1 {
        font-size: 24px;
        margin: 0;
      }

      /* Content */
      .content {
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        color: #333333;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }

      .content h2 {
        font-size: 20px;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
      }

      .content p {
        font-size: 16px;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
      }

      /* Button */
      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 12px 24px;
        background-color: #007bff;
        color: #ffffff;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-size: 16px;
        border-radius: 5px;
        margin-top: 20px;
      }

      /* Footer */
      .footer {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 20px;
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #777777;
        background-color: #f1f1f1;
      }

      .footer a {
        color: #007bff;
        text-decoration: none;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="email-container">
      <!-- Header -->
      <div class="header">
        <h1>Welcome to Trust HealthCare!</h1>
      </div>

      <!-- Content -->
      <div class="content">
        <h2>Hello <%= name %>,</h2>
        <p>
          Thank you for joining Trust HealthCare. We're excited to have you on
          board and look forward to helping you achieve your goals.
        </p>
        <p>Here are a few things you can do to get started:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Complete your profile setup.</li>
          <li>Explore our features and services.</li>
          <li>Reach out to our support team if you have any questions.</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="#" class="button">Get Started</a>
      </div>

      <!-- Footer -->
      <div class="footer">
        <p>
          If you have any questions, feel free to
          <a href="mailto:support@yourcompany.com">contact us</a>.
        </p>
        <p>
          &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Trust HealthCare. All rights
          reserved.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
